<paragraph id="F25CED90F54379F9E6C36001272FCB72" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Bergscharte</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="C3EAB98D44BA8EF3413FB2692A640E98" pageId="null" pageNumber="436" type="description">
<paragraph id="65EAA4424C2C75B5DE82848563F6196F" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="57056BC47A9F8B0950B6E56ADC8F3DF6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="436" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="8FD73842E3FE60D32945A88FE7BE0D53" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Centaurea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 436) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="775EA9CC2A5A1B944F68BEDF0BCFA9DB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
<normalizedToken id="E834B60D8573069727373809B516DFB7" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D5E1A22BDF1FECA8654E986258B43F21" originalValue="groß" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">gross</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(25-60 cm lang); 
<emphasis id="E5000725902ECF92224EB5CE5440039B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
<normalizedToken id="3418795A46DCECD420B95C7468ECEBAE" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Huelle</normalizedToken>
4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="A6601E0B04FE9A3B3F0D924629FA4502" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">10 cm dick;</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="3CBF3414F166695ABF096E92179F58DC" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
kahl; 
<emphasis id="6CD5571CED3B2D0C627B212C68AB155F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
<taxonomicName id="F0D20F047B3EF0715D20F2E6B69B481C" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
doppelt
</emphasis>
, aus rauhen bis federartig behaarten Pappusborsten bestehend (Haare 1-3mal so lang wie die Dicke der Borste), 
<emphasis id="3E630F558C31AB23C24CBF69D8DAFEBC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
die innern Pappusborsten sind bedeutend 
<normalizedToken id="AE0B64E030E782866486A69A3D61AAE8" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="5FA2B1FA07A3B46B143F7A24F60076AB" originalValue="äußern" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">aeussern</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="13D483DC77D6DB84CA44B9D782F6CEF2" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die Frucht
</emphasis>
, am Grunde verbreitert.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="85D5BE2474611A4191B1C7EA1CA889F5" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="4BB2138989ECDD23F46A5C5DDF963796" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Rhaponticum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="436" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E6E6852A73F251A5446624FDC6E91A13" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Rhaponticum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="7A1EEC18509163335B57EDCCD331FD95" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 
<emphasis id="8C5AA2FBD0500BE7517DA3CD142DA56A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">15 Arten</emphasis>
und hat ihre Hauptverbreitung in 
<emphasis id="5CD27FFD6C530AF13BA602838DBFCE10" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">West- und Zentralasien.</emphasis>
In Europa kommt nur 
<taxonomicName id="8E40714FC2BC9EE537A6C28B1953D346" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Rhaponticum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="436" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="scariosum">
<emphasis id="5B9138F8B62BB661EDDBAE31766DE1CD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="436">Rh. scariosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
vor.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
